// CoalFace — Antigravity (AG 2.0) hooks template.
//
// AG shipped a real IDE hook engine (hooks.json, confirmed 2026-07-12). This wires
// CoalFace's conductor onto AG's events. Copy this file to ONE of:
//   - project:  <workspace>/.agents/hooks.json
//   - global:   ~/.gemini/config/hooks.json      (canonical; NOT the older
//                                                  ~/.gemini/antigravity-cli/ path)
// then replace __COALFACE_DIR__ with the directory holding CoalFace's hooks/
// (a global file-copy install puts them at ~/.gemini/config/skills/coalface).
//
// If AG's parser rejects // comments, strip these comment lines — the object below is
// otherwise strict JSON. (This template mirrors the repo's platform-configs/ idiom.)
//
// Event mapping (AG has NO one-shot SessionStart — it never fires in the AG CLI/IDE;
// PreInvocation fires per MODEL CALL, not per user prompt):
//   PreInvocation -> ag-conductor.js : the standing fan-out-discipline directive,
//                    injected at most ONCE per session (a per-session tmp marker
//                    guards against re-injecting on every model call).
// Fail-silent, zero-dep, no network, no child process; the only output is the
// sanctioned {"injectSteps":[{"ephemeralMessage":...}]} JSON (the current AG contract;
// input payload is camelCase protojson: conversationId, workspacePaths[], transcriptPath).
{
  "coalface": {
    "PreInvocation": [
      { "type": "command", "command": "node \"__COALFACE_DIR__/hooks/ag-conductor.js\" PreInvocation", "timeout": 30 }
    ]
  }
}
